{"tid":2385792,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［恒大支持國安法候選內閣］insec專做小三","createTime":"2021-01-29T08:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T12:21:29.000Z","uid":177851,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"de570764ccf9d68007350a6668459e9a2de70eb0","tid":2385792,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:18:57.000Z","msg":"早前繼候選內閣主席係conday支持國安法之後<br />\n原來佢哋個insec都係冇乜良知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQdzzM9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQdzzM9.png&h=46e41b16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"green\"><span class=\"large\">俾帽原本個男朋友戴，再出軌有女朋友既對象，但轉個頭搵返原本個男朋友話要復合，仲話要第時搶人老公</span></span><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">唔單止</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"green\"><span class=\"large\">叫自己啲friend幫手作故仔呃男朋友，後尾分左手人地唔so佢就搵過第二條仔</span></span><br />\n<br />\n真係唔知揀咗咩人返嚟組隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲打睇路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06fd5a6870e4b2812fc13815e835ac70eac9d2e8","tid":2385792,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做人要有良知呢Ashlyn"},{"pid":"836528aa35c7a0f4c4591c88ad2b7b485fec7c44","tid":2385792,"uid":177851,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:20:42.000Z","msg":"估唔到小三係冇樣睇的<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5c74a52270fab7b00eb291d26ed47a4c444003","tid":2385792,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:21:07.000